      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"2560\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640696/RenderMan_Solaris_rendergeomemetrysettings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433079431&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=2560&amp;height=981\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640696/RenderMan_Solaris_rendergeomemetrysettings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433079431&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"981\" data-width=\"2560\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640708\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_rendergeomemetrysettings.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640696\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"913e6c47-66b5-46bc-be75-c91b03a30402\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640696/RenderMan_Solaris_rendergeomemetrysettings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433079431&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=2560&amp;height=981 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640696/RenderMan_Solaris_rendergeomemetrysettings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433079431&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=2560&amp;height=981 1x\"></span><p /><p>The <em>rendergeometrysettings </em>node has many artistic and technical uses and allows artists and TDs to add extra instance and prototype prim attributes to objects, scenes, lights, and collections, which can be found under the RenderMan tab</p><p>Just a few use cases are :</p><ul><li><p>Controlling Max Specular depth for glass objects</p></li><li><p>Creating and defining trace sets</p></li><li><p>Controlling the visibility of geometry or collections</p></li><li><p>Defining Matte IDs</p></li><li><p>Enabling Displacement on geometry</p></li><li><p>Geometry render control</p></li><li><p>Specific Motion Blur refinement</p></li><li><p>Dicing</p></li><li><p>Controlling volumes</p></li><li><p>Polygon and subdivision control</p></li></ul><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998DD9;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;\">\n<p>More info can be found on our <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/631308308\" rel=\"nofollow\">modelling guidelines</a> page.</p>\n</div></div><p />"
    }
